  <owl:Ontology rdf:about="http://www.omg.org/spec/CASCaRA/ontology/">
    <dcterms:abstract>The CASCaRA ontology provides a definition of data entities, attributes and relationships representing the Digital Thread.\nNote that this version of the ontology is in development and may be subject to modifications without notice.</dcterms:abstract>
